snippet.title: Roman Papush
snippet.description:
→ Join the fun @ https://discord.gg/hRDApAa
—————
Hello, fellow creators!

TL;DR version:
· I create games and various gamedev content/tutorials;
· I am on YouTube, Twitter and Discord;
· You are beautiful ✨

—————
✌️ My name is Roman, and I'm a solo gamedev-generalist/content-creator from Riga, Latvia.
Currently, I'm developing my first major game and producing videos for YouTube on everything around being a solo developer, plus an occasional tutorial or piece of original content.

—————
Links:
• Twitter: https://twitter.com/RomanPapush
• Discord: https://discord.gg/hRDApAa
• Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/romanpapush
